{"tid":1691423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]我地可以真正組織上班日抗爭未?","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T00:49:16.000Z","uid":47659,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea86074597e5f4dac0f70cd53cc58156b8f6053","tid":1691423,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"香港人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自發長期罷工永不可能成事既前提下</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解我地遲遲唔組織上班日抗爭 迫各行各業正視問題, 堅抗做港豬?</span><br />\n我知早兩星期有和你返工活動但成效不顯著<br />\n<br />\n參考返6.12, 10.31同埋6-7月既接放工/ 8-9月既午間快閃活動, 都係好既借鏡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申反對一切犯法行為</span>"},{"pid":"4dacd585aa762c3924b751e61b7d7ce1c8ea046b","tid":1691423,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"點解TVB仲咁撚串？因為狙擊Group 得個6千人follow，我今晚要見到過萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fa6fe651622bf139fbf25ca369dc755e5fc4522","tid":1691423,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dacd585aa762c3924b751e61b7d7ce1c8ea046b","tid":1691423,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"點解TVB仲咁撚串？因為狙擊Group 得個6千人follow，我今晚要見到過萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"followed<br />\n幫你推返"},{"pid":"aec58e5975c17fd36c7a9dc2581a9e62d4d36a9a","tid":1691423,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"602cefb9dee8978a8ddedd5a0761d557fdb3c64f","tid":1691423,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73741aa0e20e6d0488411b05aa667da06624d8f9","tid":1691423,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi